    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "aspnet_PersonalizationAllUsers_SetPageSettings",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to manage personalization settings for all users in a web application. It updates or inserts page settings for a specific application and path. The procedure ensures that the application and path exist in the database, creating them if necessary, and then updates or inserts the personalization settings accordingly."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple steps, including checking for existing records, conditional logic for inserting or updating data, and calling other stored procedures. This adds a moderate level of complexity, especially due to the use of unique identifiers and handling of binary data types."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "3. Input Parameters"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@ApplicationName NVARCHAR(256)",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The name of the application for which the personalization settings are being set. It is used to identify or create the application record."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@Path NVARCHAR(256)",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The specific path within the application for which the settings are being applied. It is used to identify or create the path record."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@PageSettings IMAGE",
                  "marks": [
